# Secrets — never commit. Real secrets live in ~/.config/secrets.env
# (outside repo) and as GitHub Actions repo secrets. These globs are
# belt-and-suspenders in case a future script ever writes one in-repo.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.secret
*.secrets
secrets.env
*.pem
*.key
